# consistency-gap entries. tsup/tsdown configs are leftovers from before
# each package's migration (some couldn't be deleted outright in the
# environment that did the migration — see that entry's "Known friction"
# note) and are never read by anything. Ignored so none get re-tracked or
# mistaken for live config.
